sequenceDiagram
    actor Simulator as "Demo Runner"
    participant API as "Harness API"
    participant Store as "Task Store"
    Simulator->>API: POST /tasks\nsubmit
    Note right of API: artifacts=pull_request, commit\ngithub_branch=codex/demo
    API->>Store: persist evaluation for demo-review-required-then-completed
    Store-->>API: task_status=blocked
    API-->>Simulator: action=review_required\ntarget=blocked\nverification=review_required\nreconciliation=n/a
    Simulator->>API: POST /tasks/demo-review-required-then-completed/reevaluate\nresolve_review
    Note right of API: review_decision=accept_completion
    API->>Store: persist evaluation for demo-review-required-then-completed
    Store-->>API: task_status=completed
    API-->>Simulator: action=transition_applied\ntarget=completed\nverification=n/a\nreconciliation=n/a
    Note over Simulator,API: final task state = completed
